## table card | doc="Person cards for the dev team. Explicit ids 2..6 mirror user_account ids so demo task assignees resolve by id without lookups. reset_sequence advances card_id_seq past these explicit ids so the subsequent auto-id inserts (project, milestones, …) start at 7+." | on_conflict="id" | reset_sequence=card_id_seq
### rows
id, card_type_id,       title,   email,                 alias
