## table card | under=proj_default | alias=sc_comms | doc="Comms screen (email_comm_spec Gate 7). Lists the project's comm cards directly (layout 'comms' → the generic CardListBody, cardType=comm). flow_ref points at the comm flow so the TransitionBar shows comm-status transitions; toggle_groups filter by comm_status phase (Active / Resolved) rather than task status; default_create_status overrides to 'Open' (the comm flow's create default)."
### rows
card_type_id,      parent_card_id, title,   layout, slug,  hotkey, sort_order, flow_ref,    default_create_status, alias,    toggle_groups
$card_type.screen, parent,         "Comms", comms,  comms, c,      7,          @flow_comm,  @cs_open,              sc_comms, `[{"name":"phase_scope","operator":"or","mode":"multi","items":[{"name":"active","label":"Active","predicate":{"attr":"comm_status","op":"has_phase","values":["active"]},"default_on":true},{"name":"terminal","label":"Resolved","predicate":{"attr":"comm_status","op":"has_phase","values":["terminal"]},"default_on":false}]}]`


